Contains files with data underlying all plots in the article.

File names are on the form:
PLOT_SAMPLE_MODEL_EFFECT

PLOT
qq = Quantile-quantile plot
manh = Manhattan plot

SAMPLE
art = ART sample
nonart = non-ART sample

MODEL
hap = "Classic" Haplin model including only fetal effect
hapint_cf = Extended Haplin model including parental complementary interaction effect
hapint_th = Extended Haplin model including parental threshold-based interaction effect

EFFECT
fet = fetal single dose effect
fetd = fetal double dose effect
int = parental interaction effect
